    "MHSA has quadratic complexity with respect to the context length 𝑇.",
    "In this work, we leverage large Transformer models trained on text data.",
    "Afterwards, we evaluate their ability to implement evolutionary improvement operations when presented with BBO trajectory information, i.e.",
